  m_Name: idiomas_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.Localization::UnityEngine.Localization.Tables.StringTable
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0959b9b885c06b244a4fd50d48e773b5, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 1
    m_Localized: Enter a name
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2
    m_Localized: Play
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3
    m_Localized: 'You''re walking through a forest when you come to a fork in the
      path.

      Two paths lie before you.

      One is bathed in light, with
      vibrant flowers and a peaceful atmosphere.

      The other is shrouded in
      an eerie darkness, silent and mysterious.

      An old wooden sign reads:

      "Choose
      your destiny."'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4
    m_Localized: "As you walk along, you notice the unusual flowers.\nAfter a while,
      an old man appears out of nowhere by the side of the path.\nLeaning on a cane,
      he observes you with a weary smile.\n\u2014\"Traveler,\" he says, \"I haven't
      eaten in days. Do you have any food to share?\"\nThe old man extends his hand
      and awaits your reply."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5
    m_Localized: "\nYou continue on your way. At first, everything seems normal,
      but after a few minutes, you notice something strange.\nThe ground sounds hollow
      beneath your feet. You take another step.\nThe earth begins to feel increasingly
      weak and cracked.\nSmall stones fall through the cracks and take several seconds
      to reach the bottom.\nThen you realize you are walking on very fragile ground.\n\xBFYou
      need to make a decision quickly?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6
    m_Localized: "You decide to proceed cautiously.\nYou arrive at an enormous library
      that seems to have been hidden for centuries.\nIts doors are open.\nUpon entering,
      you discover endless shelves filled with books that emit a soft golden light.\nSuddenly,
      you hear whispers throughout the room.\n\u2014\"Read me...\"\n\u2014\"Here...\"\n\"I
      have secrets that no one knows...\" The books glow brighter and brighter, as
      if trying to get your attention.\nSome shift slightly on the shelves, waiting
      to be chosen.\nDo you have to make a decision quickly?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7
    m_Localized: "You continue on your way, leaving the strange library behind. As
      you walk, the wind carries a desperate cry.\n\u2014\"Help!\"\nYou run toward
      the sound and reach the edge of a cliff.\nPeering over, you see an adventurer
      hanging from a branch jutting out from the rock face.\nIt seems he slipped
      and fell, but the branch managed to break his fall.\n\u2014\"Please! It won't
      hold much longer! Help me!\"\nThe branch creaks dangerously under his weight.\nIt
      doesn't look like it will last much longer.\nDo you have to make a decision
      quickly?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8
    m_Localized: 'You decide to continue your journey. After leaving the cliff behind,
      you reach another fork in the path.

      To the left lies an enormous treasure:
      mountains of gold, glittering jewels, and open chests overflowing with riches.

      The
      strange thing is that it''s in plain sight, with no apparent traps, no guards,
      and only a few steps away.

      To the right is an ordinary path. It doesn''t
      seem special, but it continues deeper into the forest.

      Do you have to
      make a decision quickly?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9
    m_Localized: "You continue walking when, suddenly, a silver mirror appears before
      you with a flash of light.\nIts surface shimmers like still water. Then a voice
      emerges from it:\n\u2014\"If you look at me, you will see your greatest fear.\"\nThe
      mirror remains motionless, waiting.\nFor a moment, the surface begins to show
      shadows and indistinct shapes\nas if trying to reveal something hidden within
      you."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10
    m_Localized: The fight begins
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
